{"tid":603369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【掟咪後續】網民批評沒資格退場 王晶以7個字粗口回應","createTime":"2018-03-23T16:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T01:04:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"77acea6297bdda1f7a6b51beddc4f8d072c92ff5","tid":603369,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180324/s00009/447f21d8025f5b9b58a5a2fe261cc8af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180324%2Fs00009%2F447f21d8025f5b9b58a5a2fe261cc8af.jpg&h=941e27d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導演王晶日前出席香港國際影視展的「網路發行價值再生 港片IP的破局重組」論壇時憤然離場。王晶會上說：「你們說的主題是致敬香港電影，在我看來這是網路電影集體盜竊香港IP（智識產權）。」他又說:「港片IP都是有版權的，像現在網路大電影，隨便都可以拍賭片，如果每人給《賭神》創作人1萬塊，我估計我現在有500萬...今天這個論壇是沒有價值的。」他放下咪離場。<br />\n<br />\n事後記者聯絡晶哥但未獲回覆，有關他退場的視頻網上流傳引熱話，有支持王晶但也有不少負面批評說話。昨日王晶在微博轉發了內地網民就事件批評他的留言，有指王晶「你有啥資格怒斥抄襲還憤然離場，要講抄襲你是抄襲鼻祖呀!」王晶以連串7個字的粗口作回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1521821995672&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1521821995672%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180324&d=94lPsyChUoC4HXTdeWrkd%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=e8e8d2fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1521821995672%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180324&h=4a1c2217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1521821995672&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180324</a>"},{"pid":"a10d75398153b80c7158c5a1152ccb73dde4ce00","tid":603369,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事實"},{"pid":"2be878cea78f47ae2c3b